                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium leading-[1.4] text-black mb-3">Fewer rejection cycles</h3>
                <p class="text-base text-black/80 leading-normal m-0">
                  Country-specific validation catches field errors before invoices reach the customer — removing payment delays at source.
                </p>
