                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium leading-[1.4] text-black mb-3">ERP-connected, no manual exports</h3>
                <p class="text-base text-black/80 leading-normal m-0">
                  AR workflows connect directly to your ERP and order management. No manual export-import cycles.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Slide 4 -->
          <div class="swiper-slide !h-auto flex">
            <div class="w-full rounded-xl p-7 flex flex-col justify-between" style="background-color: #ECF7ED; border: 1px solid rgba(101, 93, 255, 0.2);">
              <div>
